fea71471d171c06e6475f24993df88c078bfe79c.query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS plants
            (
                name TEXT NOT NULL,
                temperature TEXT,
                humidity TEXT,
                illumination TEXT,
                watering TEXT,
                soil TEXT,
                fertilizer TEXT,
                transplant TEXT,
                propagation TEXT,
                features TEXT
            );
